<br>
Wiz/Mag short-term DPS &gt; Necro short-term DPS<br>
Necro sustained DPS &gt; Wiz/Mag sustained DPS<br>
Enc slow &gt; Necro slow<br>
Enc Charm &gt; Necro charm<br>
Necro FD &gt; Wiz/Mag/Enc FD<br>
<br>
In short, Necromancers are the best overall caster class.  I have left most of the actual proof out of this thread because...well.... proof has so little to do with the rant boards.  Also, don't bother asking me for proof.  I don't play the game anymore, so I am unable to parse anything except the amount of overall bullshit this thread is likely to attract.<br>
<br>
Like I said, I have listed no real proof.  I expect that if this thread is going to go anywhere, it will require champions from each class that actually plays the game.<br>
<br>
Opinions?<br>
<br>
Disclaimer:  I understand that a Good Wiz/Mag/Enc is better than a bad Nec, but if you disregard player skill, the best class with the most potential is the Necromancer.<br>
<br>
